# Product Management Dashboard — Technical Test Junior FE

Frontend application for Product Management built using **Next.js** and **Ant Design**.  
This project consumes Backend API “Technical Test Junior FE Support Be” that runs locally.

📎 Repository: https://github.com/Aul-rhmn/Product-Management-Dashboard

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack

| Feature | Library / Framework |
|--------|------------------|
| Framework | Next.js 14+ (App Router) |
| Language | TypeScript |
| UI Library | Ant Design (antd) |
| HTTP Client | Axios |
| Auth (Bonus) | Firebase Authentication |

---

## ✅ Features

- Login using Firebase Authentication ✅
- Product List UI with:
  - Pagination
  - Search (title / description / category)
- Create Product Modal
- Update Product Modal
- Form validation
- Responsive UI
- API error handling & loading state
- Secure protected routes

